profile: Access Mini-Storage Ltd is a local State of Art self-storage facility in Chilliwack. We provide affordable and secure storage solutions for personal and business needs.  Monitored by security camera 24/7 plus onsite resident managers, we offer industrial elevators, plus moving dollies to help transport your items, temperature controlled, each unit has an individual alarm. We also have large selection of packing supplies from boxes, bubble wrap to covers to protect your furniture or mattresses. We are open 6 days a week and closed on Sunday and all statutory holidays with gate access 7 days a week from 6:00 am to 10:00 pm. We offer payment plans and accept various methods of payment. Reserve your storage space online or find out how much space you will need with our space calculator.
